description: Uncle Paul's Stuffed Pretzels taking your traditional pretzel and putting in a delicious twist. Starting out with the best ingredients into a soft gourmet pretzel roll, makes for mouthwatering combinations  "Chicken, Bacon, Ranch and Cheese" or a "Pepperoni and Cheese" are a must have. In Hamburg, Pennsylvania we have smiling customers with every bite, with a unique tasteful treat that will have you coming back for more!
name: Uncle Paul's Stuffed Pretzels
